Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()
    args$a <- 1/25
    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 1
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_1.rds')

    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_18.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()
    args$a <- 1/25
    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0.8
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 2
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_19.rds')

    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()
    args$a <- 1/16
    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 3
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_36.rds')

    DSC_REPLICATE <- 4
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_54.rds')

    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_71.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()
    args$a <- 1/4
    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0.2
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 5
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_72.rds')

    args$pi0 <- 0.8
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 6
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {

      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_89.rds')

    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_107.rds')

    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_124.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()
    args$a <- 1/25
    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 1
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 9
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_125.rds')

    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()

    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0.2
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 10
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)

      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu
      meta = list(theta = theta, true_pi0 = true_pi0, true_a = args$a, true_mu = args$mu)
      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)
      return(data)
    }
    data = rnormmix_datamaker(args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(data=data, theta=data$meta$theta, true_pi0=data$meta$true_pi0, true_a=data$meta$true_a, true_mu=data$meta$true_mu, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_9B2FEAE2, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/simulate/simulate_142.rds')

    ## r script UUID: 71244724
    
    args <- list()

    args$mu <- 0
    args$n <- 1000
    args$pi0 <- 0.5
    args$seed <- 1
    DSC_REPLICATE <- 10
    TIC_9B2FEAE2 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    rnormmix_datamaker = function(args) {
      set.seed(args$seed)
      non_null = rbinom(args$n, 1, (1 - args$pi0))
      true_pi0 = 1 - mean(non_null)
      theta = non_null * rnorm(args$n, 0, 1/sqrt(args$a)) + args$mu

      x = rnorm(args$n, theta, args$s)
      input = list(x = x, s = args$s)
      data = list(meta = meta, input = input)

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_1.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_1_eb_1.rds')

        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_7_eb_1.rds')

    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_20_eb_1.rds')

    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_32_eb_1.rds')

        prior = "point_normal"

        prior = "point_laplace"

    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_45_eb_1.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_58.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_58_eb_1.rds')

        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_70_eb_1.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_83.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_83_eb_1.rds')

      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_95_eb_1.rds')

    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_108_eb_1.rds')

    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_120_eb_1.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_121.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data

    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)

    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_133_eb_1.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_146.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 0
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)

    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)

        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_8_eb_2.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_21.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 1
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_21_eb_2.rds')

      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_33_eb_2.rds')

    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_46_eb_2.rds')

    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_58_eb_2.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_59.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 1
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE

    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_71_eb_2.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_84.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 1
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)

    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_84_eb_2.rds')

        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_96_eb_2.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_109.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 1
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_109_eb_2.rds')

      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_121_eb_2.rds')

    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_134_eb_2.rds')

    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_146_eb_2.rds')
    
    
Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 59275781
    library(ebnm)
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- list()
    DSC_1A3F10A5 <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_147.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_1A3F10A5$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    data <- DSC_1A3F10A5$data
    args <- list()
    args$data <- data
    args$fix_mu_in <- 1
    args$prior_in <- 1
    TIC_1A3F10A5 <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = list(mu = 0), fix_mu = T)
      } else {
        res = ebnm(input$x, input$s, prior, g = NULL, fix_mu = F)
      }
      out = list(prior = prior, fix_mu = args$fix_mu_in, pm = res$result$PosteriorMean, fitted_g = res$fitted_g, loglik = res$loglik)
      return(out)
    }
    ebnm_data = ebnm.wrapper(data$input, args)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(ebnm_data=ebnm_data, prior=ebnm_data$prior, fix_mu=ebnm_data$fix_mu, post_mean=ebnm_data$pm, g_pi0=ebnm_data$fitted_g$pi0, g_a=ebnm_data$fitted_g$a, g_mu=ebnm_data$fitted_g$mu, loglik=ebnm_data$loglik, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_1A3F10A5, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/eb/simulate_147_eb_2.rds')

    library(ebnm)
    ebnm.wrapper = function(input, args) {
      if (args$prior_in == 1) {
        prior = "point_normal"
      } else if (args$prior_in == 2) {
        prior = "point_laplace"
      }
      if (args$fix_mu_in == 1) {

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 97721975
    
    DSC_38C21C1A <- list()
    DSC_38C21C1A <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_1.rds','normal_means/eb/simulate_1_eb_1.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_38C21C1A$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    est <- DSC_38C21C1A$post_mean
    truth <- DSC_38C21C1A$theta
    TIC_38C21C1A <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    score = function(est, truth) {
      return(sqrt(mean((est - truth)^2)))
    }
    result = score(est, truth)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(RMSE=result, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_38C21C1A, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/score_theta/simulate_1_eb_1_score_theta_1.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 97721975
    
    DSC_38C21C1A <- list()
    DSC_38C21C1A <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_17.rds','normal_means/eb/simulate_17_eb_1.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_38C21C1A$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    est <- DSC_38C21C1A$post_mean
    truth <- DSC_38C21C1A$theta
    TIC_38C21C1A <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    score = function(est, truth) {
      return(sqrt(mean((est - truth)^2)))
    }
    result = score(est, truth)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(RMSE=result, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_38C21C1A, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/score_theta/simulate_17_eb_1_score_theta_1.rds')

    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_38C21C1A$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    est <- DSC_38C21C1A$post_mean
    truth <- DSC_38C21C1A$theta
    TIC_38C21C1A <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    score = function(est, truth) {
      return(sqrt(mean((est - truth)^2)))
    }
    result = score(est, truth)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(RMSE=result, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_38C21C1A, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/score_theta/simulate_41_eb_1_score_theta_1.rds')

    truth <- DSC_38C21C1A$theta
    TIC_38C21C1A <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    score = function(est, truth) {
      return(sqrt(mean((est - truth)^2)))
    }
    result = score(est, truth)
    ## END DSC CORE
    
    saveRDS(list(RMSE=result, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_38C21C1A, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/score_theta/simulate_65_eb_1_score_theta_1.rds')

Rscript SCRIPT:
    ## r script UUID: 97721975
    
    DSC_38C21C1A <- list()
    DSC_38C21C1A <- dscrutils::load_inputs(c('normal_means/simulate/simulate_1.rds','normal_means/eb/simulate_1_eb_1.rds'), dscrutils::read_dsc)
    DSC_REPLICATE <- DSC_38C21C1A$DSC_DEBUG$replicate
    est <- DSC_38C21C1A$g_pi0
    truth <- DSC_38C21C1A$true_pi0
    TIC_38C21C1A <- proc.time()
    set.seed(DSC_REPLICATE)
    
    ## BEGIN DSC CORE
    score = function(est, truth) {

Rscript SCRIPT:

    saveRDS(list(RMSE=result, DSC_DEBUG=dscrutils::save_session(TIC_38C21C1A, DSC_REPLICATE)), 'normal_means/score_mu/simulate_143_eb_2_score_mu_1.rds')
